==Trivia==
*Despite being born from [[dragonkin]] experiments, Zulrah is not vulnerable to [[dragonbane weapons]].
*Prior to Zulrah's release, a [[Poll:Old School Snake Boss Name Poll|poll was held]] to decide the name of the solo snake boss. The name Zulrah was overwhelmingly popular, gaining 51% of the total votes. The other entries, in order of popularity, were:
** Ka'nes (22.2%)
** Baloki (7.3%)
** Attor (7.1%)
** Dyzurah (6.3%)
** Duserpes (6%)
*The first player to kill Zulrah was ''SlayaMasters''.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod John C|url=https://twitter.com/JagexJohnC/status/553146510989615104|date=8 January 2015|archiveurl=https://archive.is/uasp7|archivedate=26 May 2020|quote=SlayaMasters has the first Zulrah kill!}}
*Zulrah had a festive override wearing a [[red partyhat]], [[black partyhat]], and [[santa hat]] during the [[2016 Christmas event/Gallery|2016]], [[2017 Christmas event/Gallery|2017]], [[2018 Christmas event/Gallery|2018]], [[2019 Christmas event/Gallery|2019]], [[2020 Christmas event/Gallery|2020]], and [[2021 Christmas event/Gallery|2021]] Christmas events.

